  "remarks": "Defense Technology and Science Research Center (DTSRC) was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: DTSRC is owned or controlled by, or acts on behalf of, Iran’s Ministry of Defense and Armed Forces Logistics (MODAFL), which oversees Iran’s defence R&D, production, maintenance, exports, and procurement. The Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
